  "body": [
    "Bhai Diwan Singh Maskin made a name for himself as a Kirtaniya in Bombay and he also traveled extensively to Malaysia and Singapore from the 1970s onward. Most of the recordings below are from his various Singapore tours and of his visits to Malaysia as well. According to my father, Bhai Diwan Singh Ji also performed Kirtan at my maternal grandfather’s funeral. Unfortunately, we do not have any recordings of that Kirtan as this happened before I was born. In the 1990s, Bhai Diwan Singh Ji frequently sang with Kusum Kapadia and they released several albums together. They also made a trip to Malaysia together and some of those recordings are available to download below. If anyone has more recordings of Bhai Diwan Singh Maskin to share, please contact us."
